snippet.title: Battle Waves - Official Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
WISHLIST NOW on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1965620/Battle_Waves_Card_Tactics

STRATEGIZE your units in base as enemy waves invade!
BUILD your hand with dozens of unique factions and spells to level up and deploy!
CRANK UP the difficulty and take on the "Impossible" difficulty. Do you have what it takes?
